<div class="text-center px-5 py-5">
    <h1 class="font-heading text-heading">
        primeCalX
    </h1>
    <p class="font-paragraph text-paragraph">
        A super-fast prime number checker developed by Mckenzie Regalado.
        This calculator combines two algorithms (Trial-division for small numbers and Miller-Rabin for very-large numbers).
    </p>
    <p class="font-paragraph text-paragraph">
        Note: The input should be positive integers and whitespaces are not allowed.
    </p>
</div>
<div class="invisible px-2 text-center" id="message">
    <p class="text-md font-heading" id="verdict"></p>
</div>
<div class="invisible px-2 text-center" id="loading">
    <span class="loading loading-dots loading-md"></span>
</div>
<div class="flex justify-center py-5">
    <textarea placeholder="Enter a number" id="inputValue" class="textarea textarea-bordered rounded-none leading-4 textarea-sm w-full max-w-xs h-40 p-1 resize-none" required></textarea>
</div>
<div class="flex justify-center p-2 gap-2 items-center">
    <button class="btn btn-active btn-ghost rounded-none" onclick="verify()">Check</button>
</div>